Class Game

java.lang.Object
Game.Game
public class Game extends Object
This a Text Adventure Game centered around the Hobbit and Lord of the Rings books written by J.R.R. Tolkien The player must choose the correct choices in order to get to the ending of the story.
Author:
Laviele Trias
